        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Hail.  Well, Take Breeze over Dark Pact.  Allure of Death over Breeze.  Call of Bones (CoB) over Clarity.  Lich over C2. Demi/Arch over C3.  That is for pure mana regen.  If you are in a group, and aren't hurting for mana, just use the enc version.  It saves you hps.  If you want to have the fastest mana regen possible, use your own.  It just depends on the level you're at.  Hope this helped.</P><P>Brandinimo</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
