         Clarity=  7 mana a tick<BR>Clarity2= 11 mana a tick<BR>Clarty3(KEI)= 14 mana a tick(plus wis/int and mana)</P><P>Call of bones=8 mana a tick<BR>Lich=20 mana a tick<BR>Demi lich=31 mana a tick<BR>Arch lich=35 mana a tick</P><P>As you can see our mana regen SMOKES any chanter buff.  Once you get lich or greater, even c3 sucks nutz compared to its mana regen.  Only plus is you don't lose hps, but most of our spells heal us and wouldn't be effiecnt if we were full hps :).</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
